    "content": "【PPT 03 基本规则+口诀】\n\n▲ 板书基本规则：\n前肯后否：You are a student, aren't you?\n前否后肯：You aren't a student, are you?\n\n▲ 口诀：\"肯否配对，时态一致，助动词跟着走\"\n\n【教师台词】\"Three rules: ①Positive sentence → negative tag. ②Negative sentence → positive tag. ③The tag uses the SAME auxiliary verb as the main sentence.\"\n\n▲ 举例：\nis → isn't / aren't\ndo/does → don't / doesn't\nhave/has → haven't / hasn't\ncan → can't / can\nwill → won't / will\n\n【PPT 04 特殊情况】\n▲ 特殊情况表：\n| 主句 | 反意疑问 | 说明 |\n| Let's go | shall we? | Let's含说话者 |\n| Let us go | will you? | Let us是请求对方 |\n| I am late | aren't I? | 特殊变形 |\n| He never comes | does he? | never=否定 |\n| There is a book | isn't there? | There be句型 |\n\n【易错点提醒】never/no/hardly/seldom/rarely这些词使句子变否定！\n\"He never plays football, _____?\" → does he?（不是doesn't he!）"
