  "blackboard": "┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│  Tag Questions 反意疑问句                  │\n│                                           │\n│  口诀：肯否配对，时态一致，助动词跟着走    │\n│                                           │\n│  前肯后否：You like sports, don't you?    │\n│  前否后肯：You don't like sports, do you? │\n│                                           │\n│  特殊情况：                               │\n│  Let's → shall we?                        │\n│  I am → aren't I?                         │\n│  never/no/hardly → 视为否定                │\n│  There be → isn't/aren't there?           │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────┘",
  "exercises": "【基础作业】（预计10分钟）\n1. 补全反意疑问句：\n① You're a student, _____? → aren't you\n② He doesn't like football, _____? → does he\n③ Let's play basketball, _____? → shall we\n④ She has never been to Japan, _____? → has she\n⑤ I am right, _____? → aren't I\n⑥ There is a problem, _____? → isn't there\n⑦ They won't come, _____? → will they\n⑧ You can swim, _____? → can't you\n⑨ He hardly studies, _____? → does he\n⑩ Let us help you, _____? → will you\n\n2. 改错：\n① \"He never eats vegetables, doesn't he?\" → does he?\n② \"Let's go, will you?\" → shall we?\n③ \"I am a teacher, am not I?\" → aren't I?\n\n【提高作业】（选做，预计5分钟）\n4. 写一段对话（4-6句），至少使用3个反意疑问句，话题自选。\n5. 思考：为什么\"I am\"的反意疑问是\"aren't I?\"而不是\"am not I?\"（因为\"am not\"缩写\"amn't\"不存在于英语中，所以借用\"aren't\"）",
  "reflection": "✅ 亮点：\n1. 口诀\"肯否配对\"效果极好，学生下课前还在念\n2. 情景对话让语法\"活\"了起来，有组用4个tag questions编了一段搞笑对话\n3. never=否定这个易错点通过反复练习掌握了\n\n⚠️ 需改进：\n1. Let's vs Let us的区别学生仍混淆——下次用角色扮演区分\n2. 控制练习8题偏多——减到6题，留更多时间给情景对话",
