    "content": "【PPT 03 规则归纳表】\n\n【教师台词】\"Let's summarize the rule. Look at the table on the screen.\"\n\n▲ PPT展示规则表：\n\n【板书时机——完整板书构建】\n\n▲ 教师用三色粉笔在黑板上构建规则：\n\n红色=介词  蓝色=关系代词  黄色=先行词\n\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│         PREP. + WHICH / WHOM                 │\n│                                              │\n│  先行词(物) + prep. + WHICH + 从句            │\n│  先行词(人) + prep. + WHOM + 从句             │\n│                                              │\n│  ✗ prep. + that （错误！不能这样用）          │\n│  ✓ prep. + which / prep. + whom              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n\n【教师台词】\"Three key rules. Rule 1: If the antecedent (先行词) is a THING, use prep. + WHICH. If it's a PERSON, use prep. + WHOM. Rule 2: You CANNOT use 'that' after a preposition. 'About that' is WRONG. 'About which' is RIGHT. Rule 3: The preposition comes from the verb phrase in the relative clause.\"\n\n【PPT 04 动词+介词搭配复习】\n\n【教师台词】\"The hardest part is finding the RIGHT preposition. The preposition comes from the verb. Let's review common verb + prep. combinations:\"\n\n| 动词短语 | 介词 | 例句 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| talk about | about | the topic about which they talked |\n| depend on | on | the dam on which they depended |\n| deal with | with | the problem with which they dealt |\n| look at | at | the temple at which they looked |\n| turn to | to | the UN to which Egypt turned |\n| work with | with | the experts with whom they worked |\n| live in | in | the temple in which they lived |\n| belong to | to | the country to which it belonged |\n\n【易错点提醒】①学生容易用 that 代替 which/whom：错 \"the dam on that they depended\" → 对 \"on which\"\n②学生容易忘记介词来源：不是随便选介词，而是从动词搭配来\n③whom 学生容易写成 who：在介词后必须用宾格 whom\n\n【差异化提示】A班可让学生自己造句；B班重点练\"找动词→定介词→提前\"三步法。"
