  "exercises": "【基础作业】（全体必做）\nI. 用适当介词+which或介词+whom填空：\n1. The heritage site ______ ______ they were talking is 3,000 years old.\n2. The committee ______ ______ UNESCO worked included experts from 50 countries.\n3. The dam ______ ______ the government depended would flood many temples.\n4. The plan ______ ______ they agreed saved the ancient buildings.\n5. The UN ______ ______ Egypt turned sent a team of experts.\n\nII. 将下列句子改为\"prep.+which/whom\"形式：\n6. The temple which they searched for was discovered in 1813.\n7. The people whom Egypt worked with came from many countries.\n\n【提高作业】（A班必做，B班选做）\nIII. 从阅读课文中找出3个定语从句，判断哪些可以改为\"prep.+which/whom\"形式并改写。\n\n【参考答案——教师用】\nI. 1. about which (talk about)  2. with whom (work with)  3. on which (depend on)\n   4. on which (agree on)  5. to which (turn to)\nII. 6. The temple FOR WHICH they searched was discovered in 1813.\n    7. The people WITH WHOM Egypt worked came from many countries.\nIII. 评分标准：①能否正确识别定语从句 ②能否判断介词来源 ③改写是否正确。常见可改写句：课文Para 3 \"a committee was established\" 相关从句、Para 4 \"experts investigated\" 相关从句等。",
