    "content": "【PPT 07 写作模板（填空式框架）】\n\n【教师台词】\"Here's a template to guide your writing. You don't have to follow it exactly, but if you're not sure how to start, use it.\"\n\n▲ PPT展示模板：\n\nHEADLINE: [Topic keyword] + [Action verb] + [Object]\n  Example: Ancient Temple Moved to Safety\n\nLEAD: [Who] in/at [Where] have/has [What] (in [When]), [Why].\n  Example: Cultural heritage experts in Yunyang have relocated the Zhang Fei Temple, saving it from the rising waters of the Three Gorges Dam.\n\nBODY: [Detail 1 with number/date]. [Detail 2 with method/process]. [Detail 3 with funding/support].\n  Example: The 1,700-year-old temple was moved stone by stone to a new location 32 kilometers away. The project took over a year and cost 40 million yuan. It was funded by the national government.\n\nQUOTE: \"[Insight],\" said [Name], [title].\n  Example: \"This is a model for heritage protection,\" said Professor Chen, a cultural heritage expert.\n\nCONCLUSION: [Result/Significance for the future].\n  Example: The relocated temple now attracts thousands of visitors, proving that development and heritage can coexist.\n\n【教师台词】\"You have 15 minutes to write. Use the template if you need it. Try to use at least one 'prep.+which/whom' structure from yesterday's grammar lesson for extra points. Timer starts... now!\"\n\n▲ 计时15分钟。学生独立写作。\n\n【教师巡视重点】\n• B班：检查是否包含5W，标题是否为名词短语而非完整句\n• A班：检查引语格式是否规范，是否有prep.+which/whom结构\n• 全班：提醒字数控制（100-140词），检查时态（新闻用过去时或现在完成时）\n\n【易错点提醒】巡场时常见问题：\n①标题写成完整句子（\"The temple was moved to a new place.\"）→ 改为名词短语（\"Ancient Temple Moved to Safety\"）\n②导语遗漏Where或When → 5W必须齐全\n③引语标点错误（中文字符的引号\"\"）→ 英文用\"\"，逗号在内\n④字数超限（写到200词）→ 提醒删减背景信息"
