  "blackboard": "┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│      PAST PARTICIPLE (V3) AS ATTRIBUTE & OBJ. COMPLEMENT  │\n├───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                           │\n│  V-ing vs. V3 作定语：                                     │\n│    V-ing = 主动/进行   the falling leaves                  │\n│    V3    = 被动/完成   the fallen leaves                   │\n│    判断：名词DO→V-ing  名词RECEIVE→V3                      │\n│                                                           │\n│  位置：                                                    │\n│    单个V3前置：a broken window, written language           │\n│    V3短语后置：the buildings built by Romans               │\n│                                                           │\n│  have/get sth. done（让别人做）：                           │\n│    ① 服务：have my hair cut                               │\n│    ② 遭遇：have my wallet stolen                           │\n│    ③ 完成：have the work finished                          │\n│                                                           │\n│  ⚠ have sth. done ≠ have done sth. (现在完成时)           │\n│    I had my hair cut. (别人剪的)                           │\n│    I have done my homework. (我自己做了)                   │\n└───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘",
  "exercises": "【基础作业】（全体必做）\nI. 选择V-ing或V3填空：\n1. The ______ (write) language of ancient Egypt was hieroglyphics.\n2. The country ______ (know) for its castles is Wales.\n3. The ______ (excite) tourists visited the ancient ruins.\n4. The game ______ (play) by children everywhere is football.\n5. The ______ (break) vase was repaired by an expert.\n\nII. 用have sth. done结构改写：\n6. A mechanic fixed my car. → I ______.\n7. Someone painted their house. → They ______.\n8. A doctor examined her eyes. → She ______.\n9. A thief stole his phone. → He ______.\n10. A photographer took our photos. → We ______.\n\n【提高作业】（A班必做，B班选做）\nIII. 写3个句子描述你城市中的一个历史建筑，使用过去分词作定语。\n\n【参考答案——教师用】\nI. 1. written  2. known  3. excited  4. played  5. broken\nII. 6. had my car fixed  7. had their house painted  8. had her eyes examined\n   9. had his phone stolen  10. had our photos taken\nIII. 评分标准：①过去分词使用正确②内容相关③语法正确。示例：The temple built 600 years ago is still in use. The wall damaged by the earthquake was recently repaired. The bridge designed by a famous architect attracts many visitors.",
