    "content": "【PPT 06 从句简化练习（6题）】\n\n【教师台词】\"Simplify these adverbial clauses to V3 phrases. Step 1: remove subject + be. Step 2: keep V3. Step 3: check logical subject.\"\n\n1. Because he was moved by the music, Eric composed a new piece.\n   → Moved by the music, Eric composed a new piece.\n\n2. When it was first performed, the piece surprised everyone.\n   → First performed, the piece surprised everyone.\n\n3. Although she was nervous, the singer joined the virtual choir.\n   → Though nervous, the singer joined the virtual choir.\n\n4. If they are given the right tools, anyone can make music.\n   → Given the right tools, anyone can make music.\n\n5. Because they were connected by the internet, singers from 100 countries sang together.\n   → Connected by the internet, singers from 100 countries sang together.\n\n6. When it is seen on a big screen, the virtual choir is breathtaking.\n   → Seen on a big screen, the virtual choir is breathtaking.\n\n【PPT 07 填空练习（5题）】\n\n【教师台词】\"Fill in V3 or V-ing.\"\n\n1. ______ (inspire) by the video, Eric created the virtual choir. → Inspired (Eric was inspired → passive → V3)\n2. ______ (inspire) others, Eric traveled the world. → Inspiring (Eric inspires → active → V-ing)\n3. ______ (move) by the music, the audience stood up. → Moved (audience was moved → V3)\n4. ______ (see) from the stage, the audience looked huge. → Seen (audience is seen → V3)\n5. ______ (perform) on stage, the singer felt nervous. → Performing (singer performs → active → V-ing)\n\n【易错点提醒】第4题\"Seen from the stage\"——从舞台看观众，观众\"被看\"→V3。学生容易选\"Seeing\"因为他们以为\"观众看\"，但从舞台的角度，观众是被看的对象。\n\n【差异化提示】A班可增加自由造句；B班重点掌握从句简化三步法。"
